page.content: Celebrations.In 1985 the guides celeb- rated 75 years of guiding. Guides from W Wickham and other districts went for a celebration at Crystal Palace. Double glazing, small garden with garage. 62500 pounds. Graham Denyer, Hawes Down W Wickham Pools. There is going to be a table tennis and bowls club upstairs Julia Pink, Oak Lodge Youth Centre.
